&quot;Governor Whitman announced tonight that he would appoint Travis H. Whitney as successor to J. Sergeant Cram, whoso term of office on the Public Service Commission for the First District expired yesterday. Mr. Whitney has been Secretary of the commission since its creation in the first administration of Governor Hughes. &quot;
